data.description:
Welcome to this stunning 4-bedroom, 4-bathroom gem built in 2017 located in the Eagle Lakes Subdivision in beautiful Flagler County! This modern home boasts a split floor plan, offering both privacy and space. As you approach, you'll be greeted by an attractive stone facade that adds to its curb appeal.Step inside, and you'll immediately notice the 10-foot ceilings that create a spacious and airy atmosphere. The tile floors throughout the house not only look fantastic but also make maintenance a breeze.The heart of this home is the gourmet kitchen, featuring soft-closing drawers and cabinets, perfect for the chef in the family. The Uba Tuba Granite countertops not only provide a stylish finish but also offer ample space for meal preparation.You'll appreciate the abundance of indoor lighting thanks to the 28 can lights strategically placed throughout the home.

Out back, a fenced-in yard with a lanai provides a perfect spot for outdoor entertaining. Plus, this property backs up to a serene pond, creating a tranquil backdrop to your daily life.

Located just a short drive from Ormond Beach and only 7 miles from Flagler Beaches, you'll have easy access to the best of Florida's coastline. Additionally, you'll find grocery stores, golf courses, and shopping options nearby, making this the perfect location for convenience and recreation.

Don't wait; this fantastic property won't last long! Bring your offers before it's gone and make this wonderful house your forever home.
